dmca.title: URL reappears after being taken down
dmca.body:
PLEASE REVIEW COPY OF EMAIL:
______________

 [#263897919] Your request 												 
help@google.com to me
show details Apr 10
	
Reply

Dear Mr. Hughes,

We received your letter and attached Court Order. Your request in
currently being processed and we are working to remove the URL in
question.

Regards,
The Google Team
__________________

This was sent to me on april 10, 2008 and the url had been removed but has now resurfaced. I have contacted Google, Inc. via email to inquiry "why", however no response to date.


Junius Hughes
